OL,5, A man who took revenge on his former   
OL,6, partner by murdering her mother in a   
OL,7, "frantic" knife attack has been jailed 
OL,8, for a minimum of 30 years.             
OL,10,FLorraine Mills, 63, was stabbed 48     
OL,11,Ftimes at her home in Mansel Road East, 
OL,12,FSouthampton, in November 2022.         
OL,14,FRichard Shaw, 48, vowed to "rip the    
OL,15,Fheart out" of his former lover after   
OL,16,Fshe split up with him, Winchester Crown
OL,17,FCourt heard.                           
OL,19,FMrs Justice Cutts said Shaw had        
OL,20,Fcommitted a "callous, selfish" killing.
